ontents of the graves are laid bare","transliteration":"Afala ya'lamu iza b'uthira ma filquboor","no_fn":"","text_fn":""},{"id":6156,"surah":100,"no_ayah":10,"tema":"","text_ayah":"\u0648\u064e\u062d\u064f\u0635\u0651\u0650\u0644\u064e \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0641\u0650\u064A [h:6095[\u0671][l[\u0644]\u0635\u0651\u064f\u062f[p[\u064f\u0648]\u0631\u0650","text_id":"dan ditampakkan apa yang tersimpan di dalam dada?","text_en":"And the secrets of the hearts exposed,","transliteration":"Wa hussila maa fis sudoor","no_fn":"","text_fn":""},{"id":6157,"surah":100,"no_ayah":11,"tema":"","text_ayah":"\u0625\u0650[g[\u0646\u0651]\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0647[c:14617[\u064f\u0645 \u0628]\u0650\u0647\u0650\u0645\u0652 \u064a\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0626\u0650[u:14618[\u0630\u064d \u0644]\u0651\u064e\u062e\u064e\u0628[p[\u0650\u064a]\u0631\u064f\u06e2","text_id":"Sesungguhnya Tuhan mereka pada hari itu benar-benar Mahateliti terhadap (keadaan) mereka.","text_en":"Surely their Lord will be aware of their (deeds).","transliteration":"Inna rabbahum bihim yauma 'izil la khabeer","no_fn":"","text_fn":""}]